ofxAirDigital : Natural User Interface Evolution to gesture reconizment and 3D. 
By Thierry Tournier, Maxime Coupez
Abstract :
This addon to the project open framework is a tool to create new user interface. 
This addon is divided in three parts:
The first part is not include due to license issue with microsoft and get hands coordinates from the Kinect Camera. It can easily be replace by your own hand reconizer part.
The second implement a simple gesture reconizer system, new algorithms can be easily add.
The third and main part is the User Interface, it use ofx3DmodelLoader and ofxXmlSettings. We put as many comment as we can in the code to explain it.